claim.claim-text:
15. A video image display control method used in a terminal having a function for communication with a remote communication terminal and capable of obtaining a plurality of video images and displaying the plurality of video images at one time, said method comprising: 
a first transmitting step transmitting video image number information indicating the number of the plurality of video images to said remote communication terminal; 
a first receiving step of receiving a display layout determined based on at least the video image number information from said remote communication terminal; 
a first synthesizing step of synthesizing the plurality of video images on the basis of the display layout obtained in said first receiving step; 
a second transmitting step of transmitting the synthesized video image obtained in said first composing step to said remote communication terminal; 
a second receiving step of receiving a video image from said remote communication terminal; 
a second synthesizing step of synthesizing the video image obtained in said second receiving step with the video images obtained in said first synthesizing step; and 
a display step of displaying the synthesized video image obtained in said second synthesizing step.

17. A video image display control method used in a terminal having a function for communication with a remote communication terminal and capable of obtaining a plurality of video images and displaying the plurality of video images at one time, said method comprising: 
a first receiving step of receiving display video image number information of said remote communication terminal; 
a determining step of determining a display layout on the basis of the display video image number information obtained in said first receiving step and the number of the plurality of video images; 
a first transmitting step of transmitting the display layout obtained in said determining step to said remote communication terminal; 
a first synthesizing step of synthesizing the plurality of video images on the basis of the display layout obtained in said determining step; 
a second transmitting step of transmitting the synthesized video image obtained in said first synthesizing step to said remote communication terminal; 
a second receiving step of receiving a video image from said remote communication terminal; 
a second synthesizing step of synthesizing the video image obtained in said second receiving step with the video image obtained in said first synthesizing step; and 
a display step displaying the synthesized video image obtained in said second synthesizing step.
